    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，标题用\"My working day\"可以吗？上班那段具体有哪些步骤？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "可以。上班部分有三个步骤：先泡茶，然后上楼，最后开始工作。泡茶我给自己打5分满意度，上楼3分，工作只有1分——而且我家猫会捣乱，所以参与者要加上Cat。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Make tea: 5: Me",
        "Go upstairs: 3: Me",
        "Do work: 1: Me, Cat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，工作环节是1分满意度，参与者Me和Cat。那回家部分呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Go home"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "回家就简单了：下楼，然后坐下休息。这两步都很爽，都给我打5分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go downstairs: 5: Me",
        "Sit down: 5: Me"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了。检查一下：上班三段——泡茶5分、上楼3分、工作1分带Cat；回家两段——下楼5分、坐下5分。结构对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "journey",
        "title",
        "section Go to work",
        "section Go home"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，上楼那个步骤，我想确认下分数——不对，我刚才说错了，上楼应该是3分没错，但下楼我确认是5分。整体没问题，就是再确认下标题是\"My working day\"。",
